      <title>Meloni 官员的目标是在两年内将意大利赤字降至 3% 以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/meloni-officials-aim-for-italy-deficit-below-3-within-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 领导的政府计划在未来两年内将意大利的赤字降至 3% 以下，以让正在审查意大利巨额债务的布鲁塞尔官员放心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/meloni-officials-aim-for-italy-deficit-below-3-within-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
